CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 22, 1964, pg. 6 reads: Mr. and Mrs. Clifton Victor Simmons - Harris Photo...Miss Barbara Jean Smith and Clifton Victor Simmons were married in a fashionable double ring rites at Ebenezer Baptist Church."
TitMainTitle: Groom Clifton Victor Simmons and bride Barbara Jean Smith Simmons posed on stage in basement of Ebenezer Baptist Church with crepe paper streamers
